Warner Bros has just released a new action packed trailer for Godzilla: King of the Monsters and is supposedly going to be the final one until the movie is released. The latest installment directed by Michael Dougherty stars Millie Bobby Brown, Kyle Chandler, and Vera Farmiga. The trailer shows the energetic monster getting heated and violent with Rodan, Mothra, and the infamous King Ghidorah. Consequently, that battle puts humankind in an almost apocalyptic state. The movie will be released on the 31st of May 2019. Watch “Godzilla: King Of Monsters” via YouTube below; 